that's good for you?

24:57.974 --> 24:59.498
I have to admit,

24:59.541 --> 25:04.546
I fed on a couple dogs back
in my vampire days but bats?

25:11.031 --> 25:13.207
Is it really you this time?

25:13.250 --> 25:16.079
Who else would I be,
hmm?

25:16.123 --> 25:18.604
I am who I am.

25:18.647 --> 25:20.257
Just like you.

25:20.301 --> 25:22.564
I don't know who
that is anymore.

25:22.608 --> 25:24.914
Yes you do.

25:28.831 --> 25:32.356
I killed a man for blood.

25:32.400 --> 25:36.012
You should feel shitty
about that.

25:36.056 --> 25:39.799
But you can't let that get
in the way of who you are

25:39.842 --> 25:44.107
and what you have to do.

25:44.151 --> 25:47.241
You're stronger than that.

25:47.284 --> 25:49.025
I don't know about that.

25:49.069 --> 25:52.986
Yeah you do.

25:53.029 --> 25:59.166
And you have to dig deep
right now and know it, too.

25:59.209 --> 26:02.648
It's the only way out.

26:02.691 --> 26:04.388
You're so sure.

26:04.432 --> 26:05.868
Mmmhmm.

26:05.912 --> 26:08.218
I know you.

26:08.262 --> 26:10.612
I love you.

26:10.656 --> 26:14.703
And love always wins.

26:17.924 --> 26:19.273
Liar.

26:23.233 --> 26:25.192
She lies.

26:25.235 --> 26:26.497
Get away from her.

26:26.541 --> 26:29.718
No. No.

26:29.762 --> 26:30.850
No.

26:30.893 --> 26:33.026
Don't hurt her.

26:33.069 --> 26:35.115
I already did.

26:35.158 --> 26:38.945
Shouldn't I again?

26:38.988 --> 26:41.556
Why did you do these things,
Sam?

26:41.600 --> 26:44.820
I killed Susan because
she was weak.

26:44.864 --> 26:47.606
Because she was suffering.

26:47.649 --> 26:48.563
That's not true.

26:48.607 --> 26:49.433
Yes.

26:49.477 --> 26:52.306
She was so strong.

26:52.349 --> 26:53.786
No.

26:53.829 --> 26:58.965
She was filled with pain,
just like the others.

26:59.008 --> 27:03.056
She was in the way
of the strong.

27:03.099 --> 27:05.885
I killed her to clear the way.

27:05.928 --> 27:12.718
You killed her because
you're a sick piece of shit.

27:15.895 --> 27:17.592
See?

27:17.636 --> 27:19.986
See her cower.

27:20.029 --> 27:21.030
See the truth.

27:21.074 --> 27:22.466
She's like most
of humanity.

27:22.510 --> 27:23.685
Pathetic.

27:23.729 --> 27:25.078
Undisciplined.

27:25.121 --> 27:26.209
I'm better than that.

27:26.253 --> 27:27.907
I am more.

27:27.950 --> 27:30.257
Don't listen to him, Vanessa.

27:30.300 --> 27:31.214
Shut him out.

27:31.258 --> 27:36.045
I'm not sick or crazy or psycho.

27:36.089 --> 27:38.831
I understand life.

27:38.874 --> 27:42.573
I see the truth.

27:42.617 --> 27:44.401
You're a monster.

27:44.445 --> 27:45.794
Me?

27:45.838 --> 27:47.361
Aren't you a monster?

27:47.404 --> 27:49.406
Don't let him get
into your head.

27:49.450 --> 27:54.890
Why did you not kill me
in those woods?

27:54.934 --> 27:59.852
Why did you cripple me
and leave me there instead?

27:59.895 --> 28:03.856
Because I wanted you
to suffer, Sam.

28:03.899 --> 28:10.253
I wanted you to suffer
for killing all those people.

28:10.297 --> 28:11.646
For killing Susan.

28:11.690 --> 28:15.215
Hmm.

28:15.258 --> 28:17.173
You deserve to suffer.

28:17.217 --> 28:18.479
See?

28:18.522 --> 28:20.481
I kill out of compassion.

28:20.524 --> 28:22.875
I put the weak out
of their misery.

28:22.918 --> 28:24.137
That's bullshit.

28:24.180 --> 28:31.797
You maimed me to inflict
pain and suffering.

28:31.840 --> 28:32.798
You did that.

28:32.841 --> 28:34.582
And you don't?

28:34.625 --> 28:35.975
What about Felix?

28:36.018 --> 28:40.414
What about that sick torture
you put him through?

28:40.457 --> 28:44.940
I gave him the opportunity
to grow and he did.

28:44.984 --> 28:46.812
He became better.

28:46.855 --> 28:48.204
God, you really believe that?

28:48.248 --> 28:50.816
Don't you?

28:50.859 --> 29:00.086
Late at night and alone, aren't
you drawn to become better?

29:00.129 --> 29:05.918
To rise above these
feeble humans,

29:05.961 --> 29:12.185
when the voice of truth whispers
in your ear...

29:12.228 --> 29:17.799
it is time.

29:17.843 --> 29:24.806
You are the darkness.

29:24.850 --> 29:26.808
Don't let him in.

29:26.852 --> 29:28.679
Silence!!!

29:28.723 --> 29:30.420
The humans have lost.

29:30.464 --> 29:32.814
The world is no longer theirs.

29:32.858 --> 29:34.642
They deserve to lose.

29:34.685 --> 29:37.776
Vicious, ignorant beasts.

29:37.819 --> 29:39.125
You should know.

29:39.168 --> 29:41.562
So should you.

29:41.605 --> 29:47.002
You kill for blood.

30:06.108 --> 30:08.415
I was weak.

30:08.458 --> 30:09.895
I gave in.

30:09.938 --> 30:11.461
I own that.

30:11.505 --> 30:15.857
Oh, you did not succumb.

30:15.901 --> 30:23.125
You emerged.

30:23.169 --> 30:25.998
You saw the truth.

30:26.041 --> 30:29.523
The truth of life.

30:29.566 --> 30:33.527
The truth inside you.

30:33.570 --> 30:34.658
No.

30:34.702 --> 30:37.661
You did not falter.

30:37.705 --> 30:41.404
You thrived.

30:41.448 --> 30:43.102
Don't listen to him,
Vanessa.

30:43.145 --> 30:46.366
You will save us all.

30:46.409 --> 30:47.976
Enough.

30:52.024 --> 30:53.025
Leave her alone!

30:53.068 --> 30:56.289
She's nothing, you know that.

30:56.332 --> 31:01.555
You always wanted to drink
from her.

31:02.295 --> 31:04.253
No. Susan.

31:04.297 --> 31:06.429
From the very start.

31:06.473 --> 31:08.301
Don't hurt her, Sam!

31:10.172 --> 31:13.610
That was your real craving.

31:13.654 --> 31:17.963
Ahhhh!!! Sam!

31:18.006 --> 31:24.273
You need more time...
to reflect.

31:24.317 --> 31:26.014
Susan!

31:26.710 --> 31:30.801
See who you really are!

32:07.273 --> 32:09.797
She was right.

32:09.840 --> 32:11.712
Shut him out.

32:15.368 --> 32:17.500
Dylan.

32:17.544 --> 32:21.200
You need to save your strength
for the real fight.

32:21.243 --> 32:22.897
Look at you.

32:26.422 --> 32:27.858
You've grown.

32:35.649 --> 32:40.828
You're so beautiful.

32:40.871 --> 32:42.917
I miss you.

32:42.961 --> 32:45.311
I never really left.

32:45.354 --> 32:48.140
I'm always with you.

32:48.183 --> 32:50.664
No one ever really leaves.

32:50.707 --> 32:53.275
You taught me that.

32:55.364 --> 32:57.540
It's ok, mom.

32:57.584 --> 33:03.851
Everyone dies, even me.

33:03.894 --> 33:07.246
I should have tried harder.

33:07.289 --> 33:10.989
I'm so sorry.

33:11.032 --> 33:13.121
I should have done more
to keep you alive.

33:13.165 --> 33:15.558
It wasn't your fault.

33:15.602 --> 33:19.910
You tried your best to save me
and it didn't work.

33:19.954 --> 33:23.914
That took a lot of courage.

33:23.958 --> 33:29.268
Look, I know there's darkness
in you.

33:29.311 --> 33:33.185
It's been true since
before all this.

33:33.228 --> 33:37.232
But you can do anything,
mom.

33:37.276 --> 33:39.408
Nothing can stop you.

33:39.452 --> 33:40.975
You're unstoppable.

33:41.019 --> 33:42.585
I hope you're right.

33:42.629 --> 33:44.065
I'm always right.

33:51.377 --> 33:52.987
Look.

33:53.031 --> 33:56.121
Look what you have.

33:56.164 --> 33:59.428
Keep it.

33:59.472 --> 34:01.213
You'll need it.

34:06.218 --> 34:09.743
You know what you have
to do now.

34:09.786 --> 34:11.875
Vanessa.

34:17.359 --> 34:20.101
You have to change him.

34:20.145 --> 34:21.581
Yes.

34:22.973 --> 34:24.366
Don't go.

34:26.890 --> 34:29.197
Use what you have left of me.

34:29.241 --> 34:32.374
The light you have inside.

34:32.418 --> 34:34.420
You'll find a way.

34:43.168 --> 34:47.041
Vanessa!

34:47.085 --> 34:48.825
You want a piece of me?

34:52.394 --> 34:54.309
Come to mama.

34:58.270 --> 34:59.401
Come on.

34:59.445 --> 35:01.403
Yes.

35:01.447 --> 35:03.057
I know you're hungry,
Mohamad.

35:03.101 --> 35:04.624
Come on.

35:07.235 --> 35:09.019
Come on.

35:10.804 --> 35:12.458
Come on.

35:14.982 --> 35:17.680
Come on, Mohamad.

35:17.724 --> 35:19.900
Aren't you hungry?

35:19.943 --> 35:21.380
Yeah, you're hungry.

35:21.423 --> 35:23.338
Come on.

35:23.382 --> 35:24.948
Come on.

35:24.992 --> 35:26.559
Keep coming.

35:26.602 --> 35:28.604
Come on, Mohamad.

35:34.088 --> 35:36.656
Keep coming.
That's right.

35:36.699 --> 35:38.179
That's right.

35:38.223 --> 35:40.181
Yep.

35:40.225 --> 35:42.966
Come on.

35:43.010 --> 35:44.620
Come to mama.

35:47.232 --> 35:48.668
That's right.

35:48.711 --> 35:50.670
You're almost there.

35:50.713 --> 35:53.325
Yeah, come on.

35:53.368 --> 35:54.369
Come on.

36:05.641 --> 36:07.469
Come on.

36:07.513 --> 36:08.862
Yeah.

36:08.905 --> 36:10.516
Does that smell good?

36:10.559 --> 36:12.387
Yeah, come on.

36:12.431 --> 36:15.216
Come on, baby.

36:38.848 --> 36:40.110
Come on.

36:43.288 --> 36:45.115
Come on.

36:48.684 --> 36:50.686
Mohamad, come on.

37:28.115 --> 37:30.596
Vanessa?

37:30.639 --> 37:33.076
Oh my god, what happened
to you?

37:33.120 --> 37:34.469
You have to get me
off this thing.

37:34.513 --> 37:35.296
The chair.

37:35.340 --> 37:38.168
Get the chair, the chair!

37:44.305 --> 37:45.306
Oh, Jesus.

37:45.350 --> 37:46.829
I've healed around
the hook.

37:46.873 --> 37:47.874
You have to help me.

37:47.917 --> 37:48.657
Ok, ready?

37:48.701 --> 37:50.398
Yeah.

37:50.442 --> 37:53.314
Ahhhh!!!!!!

38:00.800 --> 38:03.106
You have to-
you have to feed.

38:03.150 --> 38:04.586
No.

38:04.630 --> 38:07.328
You don't really have that much
of a choice, Vanessa.

38:07.372 --> 38:08.808
You're gonna die
if you don't feed,

38:08.851 --> 38:10.288
you know that, right?

38:10.331 --> 38:11.680
Take some blood, here.

38:11.724 --> 38:15.597
No. Not anymore.

38:15.641 --> 38:18.078
Just get me outta here.

38:18.121 --> 38:20.123
Ok.

38:20.167 --> 38:22.169
Alright, let's go.

38:26.129 --> 38:27.566
There we go.

38:45.192 --> 38:46.236
I need to sit.

38:46.280 --> 38:46.802
Ok.

38:46.846 --> 38:47.499
Yeah.

38:47.542 --> 38:49.327
Slowly.

38:49.370 --> 38:50.284
There you go.

38:50.328 --> 38:52.155
There you go.

38:55.071 --> 38:57.552
You ok?

38:57.596 --> 39:01.861
Yeah.

39:01.904 --> 39:03.471
Ok. I'll get you better.

39:06.039 --> 39:08.258
Maybe get some food?

39:08.302 --> 39:09.390
Some water?

39:09.434 --> 39:11.436
Yeah, in a bit.

39:15.440 --> 39:16.702
Ok.

39:16.745 --> 39:19.705
You're ok.

39:19.748 --> 39:23.186
Yeah. We're ok.

39:25.188 --> 39:26.189
You sure you're ok?

39:26.233 --> 39:28.061
You don't wanna rest up
for a bit?

39:28.104 --> 39:29.497
I mean, I could use the rest,
too.

39:29.541 --> 39:31.586
I'm fine.

39:31.630 --> 39:34.154
Thank you.

39:34.197 --> 39:37.810
You're welcome.

39:37.853 --> 39:39.855
So when were you turned?

39:39.899 --> 39:41.596
Back in that field
where I left you?

39:41.640 --> 39:44.730
Nah, it was way after that.

39:44.773 --> 39:48.690
Flesh saved me and...
I got taken after that.

39:48.734 --> 39:50.866
Taken, by who?

39:50.910 --> 39:53.216
By Sam.

39:53.260 --> 39:54.043
Sam.

39:54.087 --> 39:55.741
Yeah.

39:55.784 --> 39:57.525
So he's still alive.

39:57.569 --> 39:58.526
Yes, he is.

39:58.570 --> 40:00.833
He bit me and left me to die.

40:00.876 --> 40:02.400
Why?

40:02.443 --> 40:05.664
Because I didn't want to be
whatever he wanted me to be.

40:05.707 --> 40:07.579
So he switched me out
for another kid

40:07.622 --> 40:09.494
and left me in a bunker.

40:09.537 --> 40:11.583
Felix.

40:11.626 --> 40:13.976
I got out and got away.

40:14.020 --> 40:18.633
I really don't remember much
but I remember hunting,

40:18.677 --> 40:21.375
feeding...

40:21.419 --> 40:23.203
I- I really don't
wanna remember.

40:23.246 --> 40:25.684
Yeah, don't.

40:25.727 --> 40:28.643
You're back.

40:28.687 --> 40:30.471
Yes, we are.

40:30.515 --> 40:32.995
Back together again
and back on the road.

40:33.039 --> 40:37.609
Oh, Mohamad, you-
you can't come with me.

40:37.652 --> 40:39.001
The hell I can't.

40:39.045 --> 40:40.699
Not where I'm going, ok?

40:40.742 --> 40:41.787
It's too dangerous.

40:41.830 --> 40:43.876
Wherever you go I go,
too.

40:43.919 --> 40:46.226
Not this time.

40:46.269 --> 40:47.880
Ok, look.

40:47.923 --> 40:50.709
I need to know that I at least
saved one person in all this.

40:50.752 --> 40:53.494
So after everything I've done

40:53.538 --> 40:56.018
you wanna make sure
that I am safe?

40:58.238 --> 40:59.413
I know that everything
you did

40:59.457 --> 41:01.459
you did out of love
for your sister.

41:01.502 --> 41:03.635
And I get that.

41:03.678 --> 41:06.942
Turns out I have a sister, too.

41:06.986 --> 41:08.466
Wait, what? Seriously?

41:08.509 --> 41:10.337
Yeah.

41:10.380 --> 41:12.121
Damn.

41:12.165 --> 41:15.168
This is a crazy ass world
we live in.

41:15.211 --> 41:18.606
I saw some people camping out
over there in the woods.

41:18.650 --> 41:19.607
Find them.

41:19.651 --> 41:22.567
Take care of them.

41:22.610 --> 41:25.221
Do it for me.

41:33.099 --> 41:35.318
Don't follow me.

41:35.362 --> 41:37.277
Promise.

41:37.320 --> 41:41.281
I promise.

41:41.324 --> 41:43.675
'Cause I will kick your ass
if you do.

41:43.718 --> 41:45.720
Yes ma'am.

41:51.813 --> 41:54.337
I mean it.

41:54.381 --> 41:55.600
Stay alive.

41:55.643 --> 41:59.560
You too.

42:20.233 --> 42:23.323
As if I'd leave you
on your own.
